---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Tooth Fairy Tracker"
  description="Privacy Policy for Tooth Fairy Tracker iOS app."
>
  <div class="container section">
    <span class="section-label">// tooth fairy tracker</span>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: March 5, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose privacy-prose">
      <div class="highlight-box">
        <strong>Summary:</strong> Tooth Fairy Tracker does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data. Everything stays on your device.
      </div>

      <h2>Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        Tooth Fairy Tracker ("we", "our", or "the app") is a mobile application developed by Matt Donders.
        This Privacy Policy explains how the app handles your information.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p><strong>None.</strong> Tooth Fairy Tracker does not collect any personal information. The app:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Does not require an account or login</li>
        <li>Does not connect to the internet</li>
        <li>Does not use analytics or tracking</li>
        <li>Does not display advertisements</li>
        <li>Does not access your contacts, location, camera, or microphone</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data Storage</h2>
      <p>
        All data you create in the app (child profiles, tooth records, and visit history) is stored
        locally on your device using Apple's SwiftData framework. This data is never transmitted to any
        server or third party.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you delete the app, all associated data is permanently removed from your device.
      </p>

      <h2>Notifications</h2>
      <p>
        Tooth Fairy Tracker can send optional local notifications to remind you about Tooth Fairy visits.
        These notifications are scheduled entirely on your device and do not involve any external server
        or push notification service. You can disable notifications at any time in your device settings.
      </p>

      <h2>Face ID / Touch ID</h2>
      <p>
        The app may use Face ID or Touch ID to protect parent settings. Biometric data is handled
        entirely by Apple's LocalAuthentication framework on your device. We never receive, store,
        or have access to your biometric data.
      </p>

      <h2>In-App Purchases</h2>
      <p>
        Tooth Fairy Tracker offers a one-time in-app purchase to unlock support for multiple children.
        All payment processing is handled entirely by Apple through the App Store. We do not collect,
        store, or have access to any payment information such as credit card numbers or billing details.
      </p>
      <p>
        For information on how Apple handles your payment data, please refer to
        <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Apple's Privacy Policy</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Tooth Fairy Tracker does not collect any data from anyone, including children. Child names
        entered in the app are stored only on your device and are never transmitted anywhere. The app
        is safe for users of all ages.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        Tooth Fairy Tracker does not integrate with any third-party services, SDKs, or APIs. The app
        functions entirely offline with no external dependencies.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this
        page with an updated "Last Updated" date.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:matt@mattdonders.com">matt@mattdonders.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .last-updated {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-subtle);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .privacy-prose h2 {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .privacy-prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .privacy-prose ul {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .privacy-prose li {
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .highlight-box {
    background: var(--accent-dim);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .highlight-box strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }
</style>
